---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const project = {
    title: "Neural Machine Translation for Native Peruvian Languages",
    date: "September, 2025",
    image: "/traductor2.png",
};
---

<BaseLayout title={project.title}>
    <main
        class="min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-black transition-colors duration-300"
    >
        {/* Hero Section - Clean & Spacious */}
        <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-24">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <p
                    class="text-celeste_aimara font-medium tracking-wide uppercase text-sm mb-6"
                >
                    {project.date}
                </p>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight mb-8"
                >
                    {project.title}
                </h1>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-celeste_aimara"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Featured Image - Constrained & Balanced */}
        <section class="w-full px-6 mb-24 md:mb-32">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <img
                    src={project.image}
                    alt={project.title}
                    class="w-full h-full max-h-[500px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl dark:shadow-none dark:opacity-90"
                />
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Content Section - Minimalist & Readable */}
        <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
            <article class="space-y-24">
                {/* Intro */}
                <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8"
                    >
                        Bridging Worlds
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                    >
                        The Neural Machine Translation for Native Peruvian
                        Languages project was born from a deeply personal
                        mission. It was initiated by member of AiMara Lab, both
                        systems and computer engineers deeply rooted in the
                        Aymara culture, whose native language is Aymara. Their
                        vision was to build a bridge between their ancestral
                        heritage and the forefront of technological evolution.
                    </p>
                    <p
                        class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-6"
                    >
                        What began as a personal initiative has since grown into
                        a collaborative movement, attracting more individuals
                        passionate about a shared goal: translating the Aymara
                        language for a global audience. Our mission is twofold:
                        to ensure the Aymara community is an active participant
                        in the digital age, and to develop practical solutions
                        that directly benefit native communities.
                    </p>
                </div>

                {/* Technology Section */}
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8"
                    >
                        Our Technology
                    </h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                        >
                            Our progress is built on a solid foundation of
                            cutting-edge research. The current translator
                            prototype was developed using principles from the
                            seminal papers that power modern AI:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-4 my-8">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="text-celeste_aimara mt-1.5">●</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 italic"
                                    >"Attention is All you Need" - Vaswani, et
                                    al. (2017)</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="text-celeste_aimara mt-1.5">●</span
                                >
                                <span
                                    class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 italic"
                                    >"Effective Approaches to Attention-based
                                    Neural Machine Translation" - Luong, et al.
                                    (2015)</span
                                >
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-10"
                        >
                            This approach has yielded promising results,
                            validated by standard industry metrics such as BLEU,
                            ROUGE, and METEOR.
                        </p>

                        <a
                            href="https://translate.aimaralab.com/"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-celeste_aimara font-bold text-lg hover:gap-4 transition-all"
                        >
                            Try the Translator Prototype
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {/* SITA Section */}
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
                        >
                            SITA Platform
                        </h2>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8"
                        >
                            To power our models, we developed a comprehensive
                            system for corpus creation and validation, named
                            SITA. It allows us to upload sentences in Spanish,
                            which are then translated and recorded by registered
                            native speakers.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="https://sita.aimaralab.com/"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-celeste_aimara font-bold text-lg hover:gap-4 transition-all"
                        >
                            Explore SITA
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/5"
                    >
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-6 h-6 text-celeste_aimara"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    ><path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                                <span class="font-medium">Corpus Creation</span>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-6 h-6 text-celeste_aimara"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    ><path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                                <span class="font-medium">Human Validation</span
                                >
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="w-6 h-6 text-celeste_aimara"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    ><path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        stroke-width="2"
                                        d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"
                                    ></path></svg
                                >
                                <span class="font-medium">Audio Collection</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {/* Data Initiative */}
                <div>
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8"
                    >
                        Peruvian Data Initiative
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-10"
                    >
                        A robust translation model requires a vast and diverse
                        dataset. AiMara Lab is actively recovering and
                        structuring data from various Peruvian contexts,
                        including news, health, education, and legal sectors.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="https://datos.aimaralab.com/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium rounded-full text-white bg-black dark:bg-white dark:text-black hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors"
                    >
                        View Data Initiative Progress
                    </a>
                </div>

                {/* Footer Note */}
                <div
                    class="border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 pt-16"
                >
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                    >
                        Building the Future
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg">
                        This project is more than just code; it's a commitment
                        to cultural preservation and digital inclusion. We are
                        continuously working to improve our models, expand our
                        datasets, and build new tools for the Aymara community
                        and the world.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
